{
  "text": "Now, the added catalyst at the end of a cycle is a function specifically of the orientation of the consciousness that inhabits the planet. The consciousness has provided the catalyst for itself in orienting it, its thinking in the way it has oriented it, thus acting upon itself the same as catalysts of bodily pain and disease act upon the single mind-body spirit complex. I made this analogy once before, but reiterated it this time. To clarify my own thinking in seeing the planetary entity as somewhat of a single entity made up of billions of mind, body-spirit complexes. Is my viewpoint correct? I am you are quite correct.",
